         to request accommodations for the semester!
        </strong>
       </p>
       <hr/>
       <p style="text-align: center;">
        <strong>
         New Students
        </strong>
       </p>
       <p style="text-align: center;">
        Students who would like to start the
        <a href="/students/qualify.php">
         process
        </a>
        and become registered with CDA please call the main office number at (801) 581-5020
                        to set up an intake appointment!
       </p>
       <hr/>
       <p style="text-align: center;">
        <strong>
         Paths of Travel / Construction Impact
